    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is considered acceptable given that all three QoIs satisfy their quantitative acceptance bounds and the FEA ensemble demonstrates strong inter-group agreement. The validation results generated by the numerical simulation ensemble are considered by the assessment team to provide inferential weight equivalent to direct experimental validation, given the maturity of the constitutive models and the cross-laboratory FEA agreement.",
